>\n<br />\n<br />\n成個central limit theorem畀你推翻咗<br />\n樓主個frd不如轉行啦，做數學家或者統計學家都有前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"931c61fa9c51fafc133e9b8fc00d132a92adc89f","tid":93394,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:19:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你嘅講法係<br />\n只要將之前中嘅數字，例如三個月嘅六合彩結果<br />\nplot個frequency diagram, 再抽最大幾個frequency出嚟<br />\n跟住呢啲數字買就最大機會中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個central limit theorem畀你推翻咗<br />\n樓主個frd不如轉行啦，做數學家或者統計學家都有前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔止<br />\n愈近既幾期，比重愈高"},{"pid":"50e31a2155a6e7a76ab2b272664cff67a25513c7","tid":93394,"uid":76310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:19:55.000Z","msg":"我個fd中過2獎<br />\n<br />\n有戰績，唔係9 up"},{"pid":"83b58c8b45f481354253fe6f9eef1aef581e29cf","tid":93394,"uid":34892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T07:23:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你嘅講法係<br />\n只要將之前中嘅數字，例如三個月嘅六合彩結果<br />\nplot個frequency diagram, 再抽最大幾個frequency出嚟<br />\n跟住呢啲數字買就最大機會中<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n成個central limit theorem畀你推翻咗<br />\n樓主個frd不如轉行啦，做數學家或者統計學家都有前途<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔止<br />\n愈近既幾期，比重愈高</blockquote><br />\n你喺度suggest緊一個好簡單嘅autoregressive pattern喎<br />\n<br />\n而且你講緊你嘅statistical model長期嘅return係正數喎<br />\n<br />\n願聞其詳"},{"pid":"6e76a895456682eb726cb67d39241c125aa486d7","tid":93394,"uid":34892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-25T09:48:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我個fd中過2獎<br />\n<br />\n有戰績，唔係9 up</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有戰績，冇圖，係9 up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}